/479304816544714752">MailPoet recrute pour son support.</a> Si vous avez un bon niveau en anglais &eacute;crit et que vous connaissez WordPress, prenez contact avec Kim via Twitter notamment.</p>\n<h3>Structure en silo</h3>\n<p>Fabrice explique la technique de la &laquo;&nbsp;<a href="http://wpformation.com/silo-wordpress-seo/">structure en silo</a>&nbsp;&raquo; dans la construction d&rsquo;un site web.</p>\n<h3>WordPress comme une plateforme</h3>\n<p>Chris Lema pr&eacute;sente <a href="http://chrislema.com/evermore/">Evermore</a> (en), une plateforme sous WordPress.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=5ePehXuv5Mk:NhECV965jU8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=5ePehXuv5Mk:NhECV965jU8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=5ePehXuv5Mk:NhECV965jU8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=5ePehXuv5Mk:NhECV965jU8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=5ePehXuv5Mk:NhECV965jU8:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=5ePehXuv5Mk:NhECV965jU8:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/5ePehXuv5Mk" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:16;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"L''écho des plugins